text: Vilnius County is one of 10 counties in Lithuania. The capital city is Vilnius. On 1 July 2010, the county administration was ended. ==Municipalities== Municipalities are: Elektrėnai Municipality Šalčininkai District Municipality Širvintos District Municipality Švenčionys District Municipality Trakai District Municipality Ukmergė District Municipality Vilnius City Municipality Vilnius District Municipality ==References== Category:Counties of Lithuania
title: Vilnius County
